docs/resources/links.md
     1→# Resources
     3→A few resources that are helpful for building with Superstruct.
     4→
     5→## Libraries
     7→- [`bumpover`](https://github.com/doodlewind/bumpover) helps you transform data asynchronously with simple rules, whose validation API is built with Superstruct.
     8→- [micro-superstruct](https://github.com/brandon93s/micro-superstruct) allows you to easily validate your [Micro](https://github.com/zeit/micro) API request body and query string parameters using Superstruct.
